  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate symptoms control and impact on daily life from
      patients perspective using specific GERD Impact Scale(GIS) questionnaire. The another
      objective is to obtain local epidemiological data for Bosnia and Herzegovina regarding GERD
      treatment in primary care.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
